Subject: [PATCH 1/5] spi:orion:Enable spi-orion driver of armada platform

Armada platform implement orion spi bus controller, so we
need update Kconfig to enable this driver for armada platform.

Signed-off-by: Jiang Lu <lu.jiang@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/spi/Kconfig |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/spi/Kconfig b/drivers/spi/Kconfig
index 00c0240..c5c397a 100644
--- a/drivers/spi/Kconfig
+++ b/drivers/spi/Kconfig
@@ -250,7 +250,7 @@ config SPI_OMAP_100K
 
 config SPI_ORION
 	tristate "Orion SPI master (EXPERIMENTAL)"
-	depends on PLAT_ORION && EXPERIMENTAL
+	depends on (PLAT_ORION || PLAT_ARMADA) && EXPERIMENTAL
 	help
 	  This enables using the SPI master controller on the Orion chips.
 
